snippet.textDisplay:
Could the difference btw Brazil and UK be caused by a lower average viral load on exposed test subjects, due to different environmental conditions ? That should be taken into account when estimating efficacy.
Thanks again for your informative videos. True scientific information against ignorance - this is the key to improve society.
